<title>LITHUANIA: 1996 BALANCE SHEET FOR HERMIS BANK.</title>
<headline>1996 BALANCE SHEET FOR HERMIS BANK.</headline>
<dateline>VILNIUS 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Here is the audited balance sheet for Lithuania's Hermis Bank as of December 31, 1996. The Bank reported that its 1996 net profit was 27.4 million litas versus a 1995 loss of 9.6 million litas.</p>
<p>All figures in thousands of litas.</p>
